{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change distance units in road transport from miles to kilometres",
        "additional_details": "The vast majority of the rest of the world use the metric system",
        "background": "We want the Government to change distance units from imperial (yards and miles) to metric (metres and kilometres), because we think using two different sets of units is more work in the long run, and metric distances are easier to work with.",
